sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Sender Client
    participant G as Gateway
    participant C as Chat Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant B as Recipient Client

    A->>G: Send message
    G->>C: Validate and route
    C->>DB: Persist message
    DB-->>C: Stored message id
    C-->>G: Delivery payload
    G-->>B: Push message
    B-->>G: Ack received
    G-->>A: Delivery confirmation
